\[q_{\sigma}(\mathbf{x}_{t}|\mathbf{x}_{t_{a}},\mathbf{x}_{0})=\begin{cases} \mathcal{N}\left(\mathbf{x}_{t};\sqrt{\overline{\alpha}_{t}/\overline{ \alpha}_{t_{a}}}\mathbf{x}_{t_{a}},\left(1-\overline{\alpha}_{t}/\overline{ \alpha}_{t_{a}}\right)\mathbf{I}\right)&t>t_{a};\\ \mathcal{N}\left(\mathbf{x}_{t};\sqrt{\overline{\alpha}_{t}}\mathbf{x}_{0}+ \gamma_{t}\left(\mathbf{x}_{t_{a}}-\sqrt{\overline{\alpha}_{t_{a}}}\mathbf{x}_ {0}\right)/\sqrt{1-\overline{\alpha}_{t_{a}}},\zeta_{t}^{2}\mathbf{I}\right)&t \leq t_{a},\end{cases}\] (30)_where_

